com.vernalis.pdbconnector.config
Class QueryParam

java.lang.Object
  com.vernalis.pdbconnector.config.QueryParam

public class QueryParam
extends java.lang.Object

QueryParam class. A QueryParam represents a user input parameter (or set of related parameters) of a specified type. Valid parameter types are defined by the eType enum. QueryParam definitions are used by ComponentFactory to construct KNIME dialog components and settings models dynamically.

See Also:
QueryOption, ComponentFactory
